        "Task 2:Create a program that calculates the sum of numbers from 1 to a given number using a while loop.\n",
        "\n",
        "Expected Input:\n",
        "\n",
        "Number: 10"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "-3tkCkJeA3GU"
      }
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "number = int(input(\"enter a number:\"))\n",
        "sum = 0\n",
        "current_number = 1\n",
        "while current_number <= number:\n",
        "  sum += current_number\n",
        "  current_number += 1\n",
        "print(f\"The sum of numbers from 1 to {number} is {sum}\")\n"
